q{ Q:"If measuring scale has least count of 10 kg, then in 8000 kg the significant figures are" A:"b" O:a)"4",b)"1",c)"3",d)"0" R:"8000 with uncertainty 10 kg means 8000 Вұ10 вҶ’ one significant figure? Actually 8Г—10^3 has one sig fig. Answer 1." }

