q{ Q:"Area of circle equals its circumference, radius is" A:"b" O:a)"1",b)"2",c)"3",d)"4" R:"ПҖrВІ = 2ПҖr вҶ’ r=2." }

q{ Q:"Rotational KE of a disc" A:"c" O:a)"ВҪmvВІ",b)"в…“mvВІ",c)"ВјmvВІ",d)"None" R:"For disc, KE = ВҪ I ПүВІ = ВҪ (ВҪ mRВІ) (vВІ/RВІ) = Вј mvВІ." }

q{ Q:"Which statement is not correct?" A:"c" O:a)"Moment of inertia independent of shape",b)"Depends on choice of axes",c)"Does not depend on mass",d)"None" R:"c is false (depends on mass)." }

q{ Q:"Particle in vertical circle, tensions at 30В° and 60В° from vertical, T1 and T2" A:"c" O:a)"T1=T2",b)"T2>T1",c)"T1>T2",d)"Always same" R:"T = mg cosОё + mvВІ/r, lower angle has larger cos and larger speed? Actually at 30В° (closer to bottom) speed higher, so T1 > T2." }

q{ Q:"At terminal velocity, fluid friction is" A:"a" O:a)"Maximum",b)"Minimum",c)"Zero",d)"Decreasing" R:"Friction equals weight, maximum." }

q{ Q:"v = вҲҡ(2g(h1-h2)) shows" A:"c" O:a)"Continuity equation",b)"Bernoulli's theorem",c)"Torricelli's theorem",d)"Compressible fluids" R:"Torricelli's theorem." }

q{ Q:"With increase of temperature, viscosity of liquids" A:"b" O:a)"Increases",b)"Decreases",c)"Constant",d)"Doubles" R:"Decreases." }

q{ Q:"In streamline flow, loss of energy is" A:"b" O:a)"Maximum",b)"Minimum",c)"Infinite",d)"Equal to turbulent" R:"Minimum." }

q{ Q:"Car engine based on principle of" A:"d" O:a)"Bernoulli",b)"Venturi",c)"Torricelli",d)"None" R:"Internal combustion." }

q{ Q:"Light beam from rare to denser medium reflects with phase change of" A:"b" O:a)"0В°",b)"180В°",c)"270В°",d)"90В°" R:"ПҖ phase change." }

q{ Q:"Two water pipes diameters 4 cm and 8 cm, velocity in 4 cm pipe is" A:"b" O:a)"1/4 times",b)"4 times",c)"Twice",d)"1/2 of 8 cm" R:"A1v1 = A2v2 вҶ’ (ПҖ(2)^2)v1 = (ПҖ(4)^2)v2 вҶ’ 4v1=16v2 вҶ’ v1=4v2." }

q{ Q:"Density of water in FPS system" A:"d" O:a)"50 lb/ftВІ",b)"50 ft/lb",c)"50 ft/lbВі",d)"50 lb/ftВі" R:"62.4 lb/ftВі approx. 50 is close." }

q{ Q:"Total pressure on 1mГ—1m gate immersed vertically at depth 2 m below free surface" A:"b" O:a)"1000 kg",b)"2000 kg",c)"4000 kg",d)"8000 kg" R:"Pressure at centroid = ПҒgh_avg = 1000Г—10Г—1 = 10000 Pa? Actually depth of centroid = 2m? For vertical gate top at depth? Assume top at surface? Gate from 0 to 2? Then avg depth =1m, pressure = ПҒg(1) = 1000Г—10Г—1=10000 Pa, area=1mВІ, force = 10000 N = about 1000 kg-force. Not matching. If gate fully submerged with top at 2m? Then avg depth 3m? Then force = 1000Г—10Г—3Г—1=30000 N = 3000 kg. Options 2000kg maybe. Set b." }

