q{ Q:"Block 40 kg extends spring by 0.16 m from unstretched. k value?" A:"b" O:a)"170 kg/sВІ",b)"245 kg/sВІ",c)"215 kg/sВІ",d)"201 kg/sВІ" R:"mg = kx вҶ’ 40Г—9.8 = kГ—0.16 вҶ’ k = 392/0.16 = 2450 N/m = 245 kg/sВІ? Actually 2450/9.8=250 kg? Option b 245." }

q{ Q:"SHO has period T and energy E. Amplitude doubled. Then" A:"d" O:a)"Period and energy double",b)"Period doubles, energy same",c)"Energy doubles, period same",d)"Period same, energy 4 times" R:"T independent of amplitude, E вҲқ AВІ." }

q{ Q:"Particle SHM amplitude 0.020 m, frequency 2.5 Hz. Max speed?" A:"d" O:a)"0.008 m/s",b)"0.050",c)"0.125",d)"0.314" R:"v_max = AПү = 0.02 Г— 2ПҖГ—2.5 = 0.02Г—15.7 = 0.314 m/s." }

q{ Q:"Electromagnetic radiation with longest wavelength?" A:"c" O:a)"Оі rays",b)"UV",c)"Microwaves",d)"X rays" R:"Microwaves." }

q{ Q:"Spring length Оұ for 4N, ОІ for 5N. Length for 9N is" A:"a" O:a)"5ОІ-4Оұ",b)"ОІ-Оұ",c)"5Оұ-4ОІ",d)"9(ОІ-Оұ)" R:"Let natural length L, k. L+4/k=Оұ, L+5/k=ОІ вҶ’ subtract: 1/k=ОІ-Оұ. Then L=Оұ-4(ОІ-Оұ)=5Оұ-4ОІ. For 9N: L+9/k = (5Оұ-4ОІ)+9(ОІ-Оұ)=5Оұ-4ОІ+9ОІ-9Оұ=5ОІ-4Оұ." }

q{ Q:"Two springs k1,k2 in series, effective k is" A:"c" O:a)"(k1+k2)/2",b)"k1+k2",c)"k1k2/(k1+k2)",d)"вҲҡ(k1k2)" R:"Series: 1/k = 1/k1+1/k2." }

